name: UFO Money
description: UFO Money is a DeFi project working on the implementation of a decentralized crosschain exchange with minimal commissions and maximum functionality (futures and margin trading, limit orders, synthetic asset trading). In addition to the basic functionality there are farming and staking, which help to increase the liquidity of the decentralized exchange and strengthen the interest in the native UFO token, among the owners of which all the service's commissions will be distributed.
